x'=x+t, x(0)=x_0
x_0e^{t}
x_j=x_0 + \int_{0}^{t} f(s,x_{j-1}(s))ds
x_{j}=x_0(1+...+\dfrac{t^j}{j!})+\dfrac{t^{j+1}}{j+1!}
x_j=x_0\left(1+t+\cdots+\frac{t^j}{j!}\right)+\frac{1}{2}t^2+\frac{1}{6}t^3+\cdots+\frac{t^{j+1}}{(j+1)!}.
x_j=x_0+\int_0^tx_{j-1}(s)\,ds
x_j=x_0+\int_0^t\big(s+x_{j-1}(s)\big)\,ds,
x_j=x_0\sum_{k=0}^j\frac{t^k}{k!}+\sum_{k=0}^{j+1}\frac{t^k}{k!}-1-t,
